gg_cn is a pure-Gleam port of the merge engine from cnfast, which itself bundles
and adapts clsx and tailwind-merge. The full attribution chain, all MIT-licensed:

cnfast — Copyright (c) 2026 Aiden Bai
https://github.com/aidenybai/cnfast

clsx — Copyright (c) Luke Edwards <luke.edwards05@gmail.com> (lukeed.com)
https://github.com/lukeed/clsx

tailwind-merge — Copyright (c) 2021 Dany Castillo
https://github.com/dcastil/tailwind-merge

Each is distributed under the MIT License, the full text of which is identical
to the license above (with their respective copyright holders).
